snippet.title: Super Crazy Rhythm Castle - Release Date Reveal - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Super Crazy Rhythm Castle is coming to Nintendo Switch on November 14, 2023! Pre-order today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/super-crazy-rhythm-castle-switch/

Time your button presses with the music to solve puzzles and battle bosses while rocking out to over 30 thrilling tracks - including 4 songs from iconic Konami games! Can you master Gradius Remix, Smooooch, and Castlevania's Bloody Tears and Vampire Killer?

#SuperCrazyRhythmCastle #NintendoSwitch #NintendoDirect
